,38,'email_address','d.reid@sheffield.ac.uk','2010-08-04 13:53:22','2010-08-04 13:53:22'),(182,38,'message','Hello,\r\nI am a lecturer at the School of Nursing and Midwifery, University of Sheffield. I would like to ask for your support for a proposed visit of no more than 3 of my students in the week beginning 15th November 2010. It is a key aim of the course (User and Carer Expectations of Health and Social Care) that our students appreciate the scope and value of the support the SYCP offers. A number of students visited about the same time last year - and gave very positive feedback. I am trying to be a bit more organised this year, realising that you are likely to be very busy.\r\nThe purpose of the students’ visit would be to gather information about the support that is available to families at or via the SYCP. Afterwards, back in the classroom, they will then be expected to pool their knowledge with that accumulated by students who shall be visiting the Weston Park Cancer Information and Support Centre and the Princess Royal Trust Carers Centre.\r\n I would expect that any visit would take no more than an hour or so. Clearly, any visit would need to be tailored to the resources you have available. My preferred option, at this stage, is for the students to visit between 1.30 and 3.30 on 15th November 2010 – as this is their normal classroom time. However, it may be possible to find another timeslot in that week. \r\n\r\n\r\nCould you please give this proposal your consideration and let me know what you think? Of course, please contact me for any further information. Many thanks. I look forward to hearing from you.  \r\n\r\nYours sincerely,\r\nDavid.','2010-08-04 13:53:22','2010-08-04 13:53:22'),(183,39,'address','sheffield city council, new bank house, po box 1918, s1 2xx','2010-08-24 11:28:34','2010-08-24 11:28:34'),(184,39,'name','syed rizvi','2010-08-24 11:28:34','2010-08-24 11:28:34'),(185,39,'i_am_a','My work brings me into contact with young carers','2010-08-24 11:28:34','2010-08-24 11:28:34'),(186,39,'email_address','syed.rizvi@sheffield.gov.uk','2010-08-24 11:28:34','2010-08-24 11:28:34'),(187,39,'message','I am part of a group supporting the Sheffield Safeguarding Childrens Board.  I\'ve been tasked with compiling some information to sit alongside the revised Child Protection procedures that would inform practitioners. \r\n\r\nSo far our working group has gathered analysis done through the Council, ONS and Independent Reseearchers, as well as data from the Sheffield First Partnership - carers\' strategy.  However, we are seeking demographic profiling data on young carers in Sheffield that you may hold.  \r\n\r\nIf you could send me (electronically) any recent data that you think would be of use, I would be very appreciaitive.  \r\n\r\nMy telephone number is 0114 2736723, please feel free to contact me to discuss.\r\n\r\nKind Regards\r\n\r\nSyed \r\n\r\n','2010-08-24 11:28:34','2010-08-24 11:28:34'),(188,40,'address','Aw6oca  <a href=\"http://ktwpmgtlobdg.com/\">ktwpmgtlobdg</a>, [url=http://yowbwiuguktu.com/]yowbwiuguktu[/url], [link=http://vpustsyofzbo.com/]vpustsyofzbo[/link], http://vrkouuxpvevf.com/','2010-09-15 19:06:52','2010-09-15 19:06:52'),(189,40,'name','XbhETDDKJVl','2010-09-15 19:06:52','2010-09-15 19:06:52'),(190,40,'i_am_a','I would like to find out about volunteering with SYC ','2010-09-15 19:06:52','2010-09-15 19:06:52'),(191,40,'email_address','uasuek@esxlpv.com','2010-09-15 19:06:52','2010-09-15 19:06:52'),(192,40,'message','Aw6oca  <a href=\"http://ktwpmgtlobdg.com/\">ktwpmgtlobdg</a>, [url=http://yowbwiuguktu.com/]yowbwiuguktu[/url], [link=http://vpustsyofzbo.com/]vpustsyofzbo[/link], http://vrkouuxpvevf.com/','2010-09-15 19:06:52','2010-09-15 19:06:52'),(193,41,'address','138 fife street\r\nS9 1nr','2010-09-22 13:16:30','2010-09-22 13:16:30'),(194,41,'name','michaela j m barrett ','2010-09-22 13:16:30','2010-09-22 13:16:30'),(195,41,'i_am_a','Someone in my family/my friend is a young carer','